  text: Done — I wrote the 7-day rolling total formulas into cells C4:C19 and saved the updated workbook here:

`results/runs/g2b-skill-spreadsheet_gpt-5.4/train/iter_2/regression_gate/after/core_59595/output.xlsx`

The formula used in each row is equivalent to:
`=SUMIFS($B$4:B[row],$A$4:A[row],">="&A[row]-7,$A$4:A[row],"<="&A[row])`

This sums all points in column B for dates in column A from 7 days before the row’s date through that row’s date, even when dates are non-consecutive.
